Cate McGregor, now Group Captain in the Royal Australian Air Force, spent 40 years in the Army, most of them under the name Malcolm .
She was shocked when Tony Abbott told her 'it was okay' when he told her she was transgendered .
In 2012, she tried to resign from the office of former Chief of Army David Morrison when her transformation became public .
Ms McGregor said she is 'sad' that Mr Abbott is not a supporter of same-sex marriage .